Class CommandLineConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • flex2.compiler.common.Configuration
      • flex2.tools.ToolsConfiguration
        • flex2.tools.CommandLineConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LinkerConfiguration, Cloneable

    public class CommandLineConfiguration
extends ToolsConfiguration
    Support for command line specific configuration options, like -file-specs, -help, -include-resource-bundles, -load-config, -output, -projector, and -version.
    Author:
    Roger Gonzalez, Clement Wong
